<h3>Task 2.1: Define the architecture for Azure Assistant API, MySQL, and OpenSearch</h3>  
General: GenAI - Architecture - As a developer, I need to define the architecture that supports integration with Azure Assistant API, MySQL, and OpenSearch.  
<p><b>Description</b>: Develop a clear architecture diagram showing how data flows between the system components (Azure Assistant API, MySQL, OpenSearch).</p>  
<p><b>DOD</b>: Architecture diagram created and approved.</p>  
