<ul>  
  <li><b>Given</b>: An understanding of system components (API, MySQL, OpenSearch).</li>  
  <li><b>When</b>: I have defined how each part of the system interacts.</li>  
  <li><b>Then</b>: A complete architecture diagram will be available for review.</li>  
</ul>  
<p><b>Dependency</b>: None</p>  

